name: bulbasaur
flavor_text: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth. The plant sprouts and grows with this POKÃ©MON.

name: ivysaur
flavor_text: When the bulb on its back grows large, it appears to lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.

name: venusaur
flavor_text: The plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.

name: charmander
flavor_text: Obviously prefers hot places. When it rains, steam is said to spout from the tip of its tail.

name: charmeleon
flavor_text: When it swings its burning tail, it elevates the temperature to unbearably high levels.

name: charizard
flavor_text: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. Known to cause forest fires unintentionally.

name: squirtle
flavor_text: After birth, its back swells and hardens into a shell. Powerfully sprays foam from its mouth.

name: wartortle
flavor_text: Often hides in water to stalk unwary prey. For swimming fast, it moves its ears to maintain balance.

name: blastoise
flavor_text: A brutal POKÃ©MON with pressurized water jets on its shell. They are used for high speed tackles.

name: caterpie
flavor_text: Its short feet are tipped with suction pads that enable it to tirelessly climb slopes and walls.

name: metapod
flavor_text: This POKÃ©MON is vulnerable to attack while its shell is soft, exposing its weak and tender body.

name: butterfree
flavor_text: In battle, it flaps its wings at high speed to release highly toxic dust into the air.

name: weedle
flavor_text: Often found in forests, eating leaves. It has a sharp venomous stinger on its head.

name: kakuna
flavor_text: Almost incapable of moving, this POKÃ©MON can only harden its shell to protect itself from predators.

name: beedrill
flavor_text: It has three poisonous stingers on its forelegs and its tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.

name: pidgey
flavor_text: A common sight in forests and woods. It flaps its wings at ground level to kick up blinding sand.

name: pidgeotto
flavor_text: Very protective of its sprawling territorial area, this POKÃ©MON will fiercely peck at any intruder.

name: pidgeot
flavor_text: When hunting, it skims the surface of water at high speed to pick off unwary prey such as MAGIKARP.

name: rattata
flavor_text: Bites anything when it attacks. Small and very quick, it is a common sight in many places.

name: raticate
flavor_text: It uses its whisÂ­ kers to maintain its balance. It apparently slows down if they are cut off.

name: spearow
flavor_text: It flaps its small wings busily to fly. Using its beak, it searches in grass for prey.

name: fearow
flavor_text: With its huge and magnificent wings, it can keep aloft without ever having to land for rest.

name: ekans
flavor_text: Moves silently and stealthily. Eats the eggs of birds, such as PIDGEY and SPEAROW, whole.

name: arbok
flavor_text: It is rumored that the ferocious warning markings on its belly differ from area to area.

name: pikachu
flavor_text: When several of these POKÃ©MON gather, their electricity could build and cause lightning storms.

name: raichu
flavor_text: Its long tail serves as a ground to protect itself from its own high-voltage power.

name: sandshrew
flavor_text: Burrows deep underground in arid locations far from water. It only emerges to hunt for food.

name: sandslash
flavor_text: Curls up into a spiny ball when threatened. It can roll while curled up to attack or escape.

name: nidoranâ
flavor_text: Although small, its venomous barbs render this POKÃ©MON dangerous. The female has smaller horns.

name: nidorina
flavor_text: The female's horn develops slowly. Prefers physical attacks such as clawing and biting.

name: nidoqueen
flavor_text: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.

name: nidoranâ
flavor_text: Stiffens its ears to sense danger. The larger its horns, the more powerful its secreted venom.

name: nidorino
flavor_text: An aggressive POKÃ©MON that is quick to attack. The horn on its head secretes a powerful venom.

name: nidoking
flavor_text: It uses its powerful tail in battle to smash, constrict, then break the prey's bones.

name: clefairy
flavor_text: Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers. It is rare and found only in certain areas.

name: clefable
flavor_text: A timid fairy POKÃ©MON that is rarely seen. It will run and hide the moment it senses people.

name: vulpix
flavor_text: At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

name: ninetales
flavor_text: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.

name: jigglypuff
flavor_text: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.

name: wigglytuff
flavor_text: The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size.

name: zubat
flavor_text: Forms colonies in perpetually dark places. Uses ultrasonic waves to identify and approach targets.

name: golbat
flavor_text: Once it strikes, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly.

name: oddish
flavor_text: During the day, it keeps its face buried in the ground. At night, it wanders around sowing its seeds.

name: gloom
flavor_text: The fluid that oozes from its mouth isn't drool. It is a nectar that is used to attract prey.

name: vileplume
flavor_text: It has the worldâs largest petals. With every step, the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.

name: paras

name: parasect
flavor_text: A host-parasite pair in which the parasite mushroom has taken over the host bug. Prefers damp places.

name: venonat
flavor_text: Lives in the shadows of tall trees where it eats insects. It is attracted by light at night.

name: venomoth
flavor_text: The dustlike scales covering its wings are color-coded to indicate the kinds of poison it has.

name: diglett
flavor_text: Lives about one yard underground where it feeds on plant roots. It sometimes appears above ground.

name: dugtrio
flavor_text: A team of DIGLETT triplets. It triggers huge earthquakes by burrowing 60 miles underground.

name: meowth
flavor_text: It washes its face regularly to keep the coin on its forehead spotless. It doesnât get along with Galarian Meowth.

name: persian
flavor_text: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.

name: psyduck
flavor_text: While lulling its enemies with its vacant look, this wily POKÃ©MON will use psychokinetic powers.

name: golduck
flavor_text: Often seen swimÂ­ ming elegantly by lake shores. It is often mistaken for the Japanese monster, Kappa.

name: mankey
flavor_text: Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile one moment then thrashing away the next instant.

name: primeape
flavor_text: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.

name: growlithe
flavor_text: Very protective of its territory. It will bark and bite to repel intruders from its space.

name: arcanine
flavor_text: A POKÃ©MON that has been admired since the past for its beauty. It runs agilely as if on wings.

name: poliwag
flavor_text: Its newly grown legs prevent it from running. It appears to prefer swimming than trying to stand.

name: poliwhirl
flavor_text: Capable of living in or out of water. When out of water, it sweats to keep its body slimy.

name: poliwrath
flavor_text: An adept swimmer at both the front crawl and breast stroke. Easily overtakes the best human swimmers.

name: abra
flavor_text: Using its ability to read minds, it will identify impending danger and TELEPORT to safety.

name: kadabra
flavor_text: It emits special alpha waves from its body that induce headaches just by being close by.

name: alakazam
flavor_text: Its brain can outÂ­ perform a superÂ­ computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

name: machop
flavor_text: Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger.

name: machoke
flavor_text: Its muscular body is so powerful, it must wear a power save belt to be able to regulate its motions.

name: machamp
flavor_text: Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punches that can send the victim clear over the horizon.

name: bellsprout
flavor_text: A carnivorous POKÃ©MON that traps and eats bugs. It uses its root feet to soak up needed moisture.

name: weepinbell
flavor_text: It spits out POISONPOWDER to immobilize the enemy and then finishes it with a spray of ACID.

name: victreebel
flavor_text: Said to live in huge colonies deep in jungles, although no one has ever returned from there.

name: tentacool
flavor_text: Drifts in shallow seas. Anglers who hook them by accident are often punished by its stinging acid.

name: tentacruel
flavor_text: The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey.

name: geodude
flavor_text: Found in fields and mountains. Mistaking them for boulders, people often step or trip on them.

name: graveler
flavor_text: Rolls down slopes to move. It rolls over any obstacle without slowing or changing its direction.

name: golem
flavor_text: Its boulder-like body is extremely hard. It can easily withstand dynamite blasts without damage.

name: ponyta
flavor_text: Its hooves are 10 times harder than diamonds. It can trample anything completely flat in little time.

name: rapidash
flavor_text: Very competitive, this POKÃ©MON will chase anything that moves fast in the hopes of racing it.

name: slowpoke
flavor_text: Incredibly slow and dopey. It takes 5 seconds for it to feel pain when under attack.

name: slowbro
flavor_text: The SHELLDER that is latched onto SLOWPOKE's tail is said to feed on the host's left over scraps.

name: magnemite
flavor_text: Uses anti-gravity to stay suspended. Appears without warning and uses THUNDER WAVE and similar moves.

name: magneton
flavor_text: Formed by several MAGNEMITEs linked together. They frequently appear when sunspots flare up.

name: farfetchd
flavor_text: The sprig of green onions it holds is its weapon. It is used much like a metal sword.

name: doduo
flavor_text: A bird that makes up for its poor flying with its fast foot speed. Leaves giant footprints.

name: dodrio
flavor_text: Uses its three brains to execute complex plans. While two heads sleep, one head stays awake.

name: seel
flavor_text: The protruding horn on its head is very hard. It is used for bashing through thick ice.

name: dewgong
flavor_text: Stores thermal energy in its body. Swims at a steady 8 knots even in intensely cold waters.

name: grimer
flavor_text: Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.

name: muk
flavor_text: Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison.

name: shellder
flavor_text: Its hard shell repels any kind of attack. It is vulnerable only when its shell is open.

name: cloyster
flavor_text: When attacked, it launches its horns in quick volleys. Its innards have never been seen.

name: gastly
flavor_text: Almost invisible, this gaseous POKÃ©MON cloaks the target and puts it to sleep without notice.

name: haunter
flavor_text: Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from anÂ­ other dimension.

name: gengar
flavor_text: Under a full moon, this POKÃ©MON likes to mimic the shadows of people and laugh at their fright.

name: onix
flavor_text: As it grows, the stone portions of its body harden to become similar to a diamond, but colored black.

name: drowzee
flavor_text: Puts enemies to sleep then eats their dreams. Occasionally gets sick from eating bad dreams.

name: hypno
flavor_text: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION.

name: krabby
flavor_text: Its pincers are not only powerful weapons, they are used for balance when walking sideways.

name: kingler
flavor_text: The large pincer has 10000 hp of crushing power. However, its huge size makes it unwieldy to use.

name: voltorb
flavor_text: Usually found in power plants. Easily mistaken for a POKÃ© BALL, they have zapped many people.

name: electrode
flavor_text: It stores electric energy under very high pressure. It often explodes with little or no provocation.

name: exeggcute
flavor_text: Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they quickly gather and attack in swarms.

name: exeggutor
flavor_text: Legend has it that on rare occasions, one of its heads will drop off and continue on as an EXEGGCUTE.

name: cubone
flavor_text: Because it never removes its skull helmet, no one has ever seen this POKÃ©MON's real face.

name: marowak
flavor_text: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws the bone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.

name: hitmonlee
flavor_text: When in a hurry, its legs lengthen progressively. It runs smoothly with extra long, loping strides.

name: hitmonchan
flavor_text: While apparently doing nothing, it fires punches in lightning fast volleys that are impossible to see.

name: lickitung
flavor_text: Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon's. It leaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies.

name: koffing
flavor_text: Because it stores several kinds of toxic gases in its body, it is prone to exploding without warning.

name: weezing
flavor_text: Where two kinds of poison gases meet, 2 KOFFINGs can fuse into a WEEZING over many years.

name: rhyhorn
flavor_text: A POKÃ©MON with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won't stop running until it falls asleep.

name: rhydon
flavor_text: Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees.

name: chansey
flavor_text: A rare and elusive POKÃ©MON that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.

name: tangela
flavor_text: The whole body is swathed with wide vines that are similar to seaÂ­ weed. Its vines shake as it walks.

name: kangaskhan
flavor_text: The infant rarely ventures out of its mother's protective pouch until it is 3 years old.

name: horsea
flavor_text: Known to shoot down flying bugs with precision blasts of ink from the surface of the water.

name: seadra
flavor_text: Capable of swimÂ­ ming backwards by rapidly flapping its wing-like pectoral fins and stout tail.

name: goldeen
flavor_text: Its tail fin billows like an elegant ballroom dress, giving it the nickname of the Water Queen.

name: seaking
flavor_text: In the autumn spawning season, they can be seen swimming powerfully up rivers and creeks.

name: staryu
flavor_text: If its body is torn, it can grow back if the red core remains. The core flashes at midnight.

name: starmie
flavor_text: Its central core glows with the seven colors of the rainbow. Some people value the core as a gem.

name: mr.mime
flavor_text: If interrupted while it is miming, it will slap around the offender with its broad hands.

name: scyther
flavor_text: With ninja-like agility and speed, it can create the illusion that there is more than one.

name: jynx
flavor_text: It seductively wiggles its hips as it walks. It can cause people to dance in unison with it.

name: electabuzz
flavor_text: Normally found near power plants, they can wander away and cause major blackouts in cities.

name: magmar
flavor_text: Its body always burns with an orange glow that enables it to hide perfectly among flames.

name: pinsir
flavor_text: If it fails to crush the victim in its pincers, it will swing it around and toss it hard.

name: tauros
flavor_text: When it targets an enemy, it charges furiously while whipping its body with its long tails.

name: magikarp
flavor_text: In the distant past, it was somewhat stronger than the horribly weak descendants that exist today.

name: gyarados
flavor_text: Once it begins to rampage, a GYARADOS will burn everything down, even in a harsh storm.

name: lapras
flavor_text: A POKÃ©MON that has been overÂ­ hunted almost to extinction. It can ferry people across the water.

name: ditto
flavor_text: Capable of copying an enemy's genetic code to instantly transform itself into a duplicate of the enemy.

name: eevee
flavor_text: Its genetic code is irregular. It may mutate if it is exposed to radiation from element STONEs.

name: vaporeon
flavor_text: Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid's.

name: jolteon
flavor_text: It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10000- volt lightning bolts.

name: flareon
flavor_text: When storing thermal energy in its body, its temperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.

name: porygon
flavor_text: A POKÃ©MON that consists entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace.

name: omanyte
flavor_text: Although long extinct, in rare cases, it can be genetically resurrected from fossils.

name: omastar
flavor_text: A prehistoric POKÃ©MON that died out when its heavy shell made it impossible to catch prey.

name: kabuto
flavor_text: A POKÃ©MON that was resurrected from a fossil found in what was once the ocean floor eons ago.

name: kabutops
flavor_text: Its sleek shape is perfect for swimÂ­ ming. It slashes prey with its claws and drains the body fluids.

name: aerodactyl
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.

name: snorlax
flavor_text: Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.

name: articuno
flavor_text: A legendary bird POKÃ©MON that is said to appear to doomed people who are lost in icy mountains.

name: zapdos
flavor_text: A legendary bird POKÃ©MON that is said to appear from clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.

name: moltres
flavor_text: Known as the legendary bird of fire. Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flash of flames.

name: dratini
flavor_text: Long considered a mythical POKÃ©MON until recently when a small colony was found living underwater.

name: dragonair
flavor_text: A mystical POKÃ©MON that exudes a gentle aura. Has the ability to change climate conditions.

name: dragonite
flavor_text: An extremely rarely seen marine POKÃ©MON. Its intelligence is said to match that of humans.

name: mewtwo
flavor_text: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

name: mew
flavor_text: So rare that it is still said to be a mirage by many experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.

name: chikorita
flavor_text: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on its head. It is docile and loves to soak up the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
flavor_text: The scent of spices comes from around its neck. Somehow, sniffing it makes you want to fight.

name: meganium
flavor_text: The aroma that rises from its petals contains a substance that calms aggressive feelings.

name: cyndaquil
flavor_text: It has a timid nature. If it is startled, the flames on its back burn more vigorously.

name: quilava
flavor_text: Be careful if it turns its back during battle. It means that it will attack with the fire on its back.

name: typhlosion
flavor_text: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything that touches it will instantly go up in flames.

name: totodile
flavor_text: Its well-developed jaws are powerful and capable of crushing anything. Even its trainer must be careful.

name: croconaw
flavor_text: If it loses a fang, a new one grows back in its place. There are always 48 fangs lining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
flavor_text: When it bites with its massive and powerful jaws, it shakes its head and savagely tears its victim up.

name: sentret
flavor_text: A very cautious POKÃ©MON, it raises itself up using its tail to get a better view of its surroundings.

name: furret
flavor_text: It makes a nest to suit its long and skinny body. The nest is impossible for other POKÃ©MON to enter.

name: hoothoot
flavor_text: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet so fast, the movement can rarely be seen.

name: noctowl
flavor_text: Its eyes are specially adapted. They concentrate even faint light and enable it to see in the dark.

name: ledyba
flavor_text: It is very timid. It will be afraid to move if it is alone. But it will be active if it is in a group.

name: ledian
flavor_text: When the stars flicker in the night sky, it flutters about, scattering a glowing powder.

name: spinarak
flavor_text: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web, waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ariados
flavor_text: It spins string not only from its rear but also from its mouth. It is hard to tell which end is which.

name: crobat
flavor_text: It flies so siÂ­ lently through the dark on its four wings that it may not be noticed even when nearby.

name: chinchou
flavor_text: Chinchou blink their shining antennae at one another to claim their respective turf.

name: lanturn
flavor_text: The light it emits is so bright that it can illuminate the sea's surface from a depth of over three miles.

name: pichu
flavor_text: It is not yet skilled at storing electricity. It may send out a jolt if amused or startled.

name: cleffa
flavor_text: Because of its unusual, star-like silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor.

name: igglybuff
flavor_text: It has a very soft body. If it starts to roll, it will bounce all over and be impossible to stop.

name: togepi
flavor_text: The shell seems to be filled with joy. It is said that it will share good luck when treated kindly.

name: togetic
flavor_text: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, carÂ­ ing people and shower them with happiness.

name: natu
flavor_text: Because its wings aren't yet fully grown, it has to hop to get around. It is always starÂ­ ing at something.

name: xatu
flavor_text: They say that it stays still and quiet because it is seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: mareep
flavor_text: If static elecÂ­ tricity builds in its body, its fleece doubles in volume. Touching it will shock you.

name: flaaffy
flavor_text: As a result of storing too much electricity, it developed patches where even downy wool won't grow.

name: ampharos
flavor_text: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seen from far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

name: bellossom
flavor_text: Plentiful in the tropics. When it dances, its petals rub together and make a pleasant ringing sound.

name: marill
flavor_text: The tip of its tail, which conÂ­ tains oil that is lighter than waÂ­ ter, lets it swim without drowning.

name: azumarill
flavor_text: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.

name: sudowoodo
flavor_text: Although it always pretends to be a tree, its composiÂ­ tion appears to be closer to a rock than a plant.

name: politoed
flavor_text: If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, they respond by gatherÂ­ ing from far and wide.

name: hoppip
flavor_text: To keep from being blown away by the wind, they gather in clusters. They do enjoy gentle breezes, though.

name: skiploom
flavor_text: The bloom on top of its head opens and closes as the temperature flucÂ­ tuates up and down.

name: jumpluff
flavor_text: Once it catches the wind, it deftÂ­ ly controls its cotton-puff spores to float, even around the world.

name: aipom
flavor_text: Its tail is so powerful that it can use it to grab a tree branch and hold itself up in the air.

name: sunkern
flavor_text: It may drop out of the sky suddenly. If attacked by a SPEAROW, it will violently shake its leaves.

name: sunflora
flavor_text: It converts sunÂ­ light into energy. In the darkness after sunset, it closes its petals and becomes still.

name: yanma
flavor_text: If it flaps its wings really fast, it can generate shock waves that will shatter winÂ­ dows in the area.

name: wooper
flavor_text: This POKÃ©MON lives in cold water. It will leave the water to search for food when it gets cold outside.

name: quagsire
flavor_text: This carefree POKÃ©MON has an easy-going nature. While swimming, it always bumps into boat hulls.

name: espeon
flavor_text: It uses the fine hair that covers its body to sense air currents and predict its eneÂ­ my's actions.

name: umbreon
flavor_text: When agitated, this POKÃ©MON proÂ­ tects itself by spraying poisonous sweat from its pores.

name: murkrow
flavor_text: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: slowking
flavor_text: It has incredible intellect and inÂ­ tuition. Whatever the situation, it remains calm and collected.

name: misdreavus
flavor_text: It likes playing mischievous tricks such as screaming and wailing to startle people at night.

name: unown
flavor_text: Their shapes look like hieroglyphs on ancient tabÂ­ lets. It is said that the two are somehow related.

name: wobbuffet
flavor_text: It hates light and shock. If attackÂ­ ed, it inflates its body to pump up its counterÂ­ strike.

name: girafarig
flavor_text: Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent and bite.

name: pineco
flavor_text: It likes to make its shell thicker by adding layers of tree bark. The additional weight doesn't bother it.

name: forretress
flavor_text: Its entire body is shielded by a steel-hard shell. What lurks inside the armor is a total mystery.

name: dunsparce
flavor_text: When spotted, this POKÃ©MON escapes backward by furiÂ­ ously boring into the ground with its tail.

name: gligar
flavor_text: It flies straight at its target's face then clamps down on the starÂ­ tled victim to inject poison.

name: steelix
flavor_text: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.

name: snubbull
flavor_text: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind and affectionate. It is very popular among women.

name: granbull
flavor_text: It is actually timid and easily spooked. If atÂ­ tacked, it flails about to fend off its attacker.

name: qwilfish
flavor_text: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its body by drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

name: scizor
flavor_text: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

name: shuckle
flavor_text: The BERRIES it stores in its vase-like shell decompose and become a gooey liquid.

name: heracross
flavor_text: It is usually docile, but if it is disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn.

name: sneasel
flavor_text: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sudÂ­ denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

name: teddiursa
flavor_text: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It always licks its paws because they are soaked with honey.

name: ursaring
flavor_text: Although it is a good climber, it prefers to snap trees with its forelegs and eat fallen BERRIES.

name: slugma
flavor_text: It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because if it stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.

name: magcargo
flavor_text: The shell on its back is just skin that has cooled and hardened. It breaks easily with a slight touch.

name: swinub
flavor_text: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig up food. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

name: piloswine
flavor_text: Because the long hair all over its body obscures its sight, it just keeps charging repeatedly.

name: corsola
flavor_text: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

name: remoraid
flavor_text: It has superb acÂ­ curacy. The water it shoots out can strike even moving prey from more than 300 feet.

name: octillery
flavor_text: It traps enemies with its suction- cupped tentacles then smashes them with its rock-hard head.

name: delibird
flavor_text: It carries food all day long. There are tales about lost people who were saved by the food it had.

name: mantine
flavor_text: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if REMORAID attach to it for scavenging its leftovers.

name: skarmory
flavor_text: Its sturdy wings look heavy, but they are actually hollow and light, allowing it to fly freely in the sky.

name: houndour
flavor_text: It uses different kinds of cries for communicating with others of its kind and for pursuing its prey.

name: houndoom
flavor_text: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from its mouth, the pain will never go away.

name: kingdra
flavor_text: It is said that it usually hides in underwater caves. It can create whirlpools by yawning.

name: phanpy
flavor_text: It swings its long snout around playÂ­ fully, but because it is so strong, that can be danÂ­ gerous.

name: donphan
flavor_text: It has sharp, hard tusks and a rugged hide. Its TACKLE is strong enough to knock down a house.

name: porygon2
flavor_text: This upgraded version of PORYGON is designed for space exploration. It can't fly, though.

name: stantler
flavor_text: The curved antlers subtly change the flow of air to create a strange space where realÂ­ ity is distorted.

name: smeargle
flavor_text: A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.

name: tyrogue
flavor_text: It is always bursting with enÂ­ ergy. To make itÂ­ self stronger, it keeps on fighting even if it loses.

name: hitmontop
flavor_text: If you become enchanted by its smooth, elegant, dance-like kicks, you may get drilled hard.

name: smoochum
flavor_text: Its lips are the most sensitive parts on its body. It always uses its lips first to examine things.

name: elekid
flavor_text: It rotates its arms to generate electricity, but it tires easily, so it charges up only a little bit.

name: magby
flavor_text: Each and every time it inhales and exhales, hot embers dribble out of its mouth and nostrils.

name: miltank
flavor_text: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it the ultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

name: blissey
flavor_text: Anyone who takes even one bite of BLISSEY's egg beÂ­ comes unfailingly caring and pleasÂ­ ant to everyone.

name: raikou
flavor_text: The rain clouds it carries let it fire thunderbolts at will. They say that it descended with lightning.

name: entei
flavor_text: Volcanoes erupt when it barks. UnÂ­ able to restrain its extreme power, it races headlong around the land.

name: suicune
flavor_text: It races around the world to purify fouled water. It dashes away with the north wind.

name: larvitar
flavor_text: It feeds on soil. After it has eaten a large mountain, it will fall asleep so it can grow.

name: pupitar
flavor_text: Its shell is as hard as sheet rock, and it is also very strong. Its THRASHING can topple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
flavor_text: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so it is very eager to make challenges against enemies.

name: lugia
flavor_text: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at the bottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

name: ho-oh
flavor_text: Legends claim this POKÃ©MON flies the world's skies conÂ­ tinuously on its magnificent seven- colored wings.

name: celebi
flavor_text: This POKÃ©MON wanÂ­ ders across time. Grass and trees flourish in the forests in which it has appeared.

name: treecko
flavor_text: TREECKO has small hooks on the bottom of its feet that enable it to scale vertical walls. This POKÃ©MON attacks by slamming foes with its thick tail.

name: grovyle
flavor_text: The leaves growing out of GROVYLEâs body are convenient for camouflaging it from enemies in the forest. This POKÃ©MON is a master at climbing trees in jungles.

name: sceptile
flavor_text: The leaves growing on SCEPTILEâs body are very sharp edged. This POKÃ©MON is very agile - it leaps all over the branches of trees and jumps on its foe from above or behind.

name: torchic
flavor_text: TORCHIC sticks with its TRAINER, following behind with unsteady steps. This POKÃ©MON breathes fire of over 1,800 degrees F, including fireballs that leave the foe scorched black.

name: combusken
flavor_text: COMBUSKEN toughens up its legs and thighs by running through fields and mountains. This POKÃ©MONâs legs possess both speed and power, enabling it to dole out ten kicks in one second.

name: blaziken
flavor_text: In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense flames from its wrists and attacks foes courageously. The stronger the foe, the more intensely this POKÃ©MONâs wrists burn.

name: mudkip
flavor_text: The fin on MUDKIPâs head acts as highly sensitive radar. Using this fin to sense movements of water and air, this POKÃ©MON can determine what is taking place around it without using its eyes.

name: marshtomp
flavor_text: The surface of MARSHTOMPâs body is enveloped by a thin, sticky film that enables it to live on land. This POKÃ©MON plays in mud on beaches when the ocean tide is low.

name: swampert
flavor_text: SWAMPERT is very strong. It has enough power to easily drag a boulder weighing more than a ton. This POKÃ©MON also has powerful vision that lets it see even in murky water.

name: poochyena
flavor_text: At first sight, POOCHYENA takes a bite at anything that moves. This POKÃ©MON chases after prey until the victim becomes exhausted. However, it may turn tail if the prey strikes back.

name: mightyena
flavor_text: MIGHTYENA gives obvious signals when it is preparing to attack. It starts to growl deeply and then flattens its body. This POKÃ©MON will bite savagely with its sharply pointed fangs.

name: zigzagoon
flavor_text: ZIGZAGOON restlessly wanders everywhere at all times. This POKÃ©MON does so because it is very curious. It becomes interested in anything that it happens to see.

name: linoone
flavor_text: LINOONE always runs full speed and only in straight lines. If facing an obstacle, it makes a right-angle turn to evade it. This POKÃ©MON is very challenged by gently curving roads.

name: wurmple
flavor_text: Using the spikes on its rear end, WURMPLE peels the bark off trees and feeds on the sap that oozes out. This POKÃ©MONâs feet are tipped with suction pads that allow it to cling to glass without slipping.

name: silcoon
flavor_text: SILCOON tethers itself to a tree branch using silk to keep from falling. There, this POKÃ©MON hangs quietly while it awaits evolution. It peers out of the silk cocoon through a small hole.

name: beautifly
flavor_text: BEAUTIFLYâs favorite food is the sweet pollen of flowers. If you want to see this POKÃ©MON, just leave a potted flower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY is sure to come looking for pollen.

name: cascoon
flavor_text: CASCOON makes its protective cocoon by wrapping its body entirely with a fine silk from its mouth. Once the silk goes around its body, it hardens. This POKÃ©MON prepares for its evolution inside the cocoon.

name: dustox
flavor_text: DUSTOX is instinctively drawn to light. Swarms of this POKÃ©MON are attracted by the bright lights of cities, where they wreak havoc by stripping the leaves off roadside trees for food.

name: lotad
flavor_text: It searches about for clean water. If it does not drink water for too long, the leaf on its head wilts.

name: lombre
flavor_text: It lives at the waterâs edge where it is sunny. It sleeps on a bed of water grass by day and becomes active at night.

name: ludicolo
flavor_text: LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon as it hears cheerful, festive music. This POKÃ©MON is said to appear when it hears the singing of children on hiking outings.

name: seedot
flavor_text: SEEDOT attaches itself to a tree branch using the top of its head. It sucks moisture from the tree while hanging off the branch. The more water it drinks, the glossier this POKÃ©MONâs body becomes.

name: nuzleaf
flavor_text: NUZLEAF live in densely overgrown forests. They occasionally venture out of the forest to startle people. This POKÃ©MON dislikes having its long nose pinched.

name: shiftry
flavor_text: It lives quietly in the deep forest. It is said to create chilly winter winds with the fans it holds.

name: taillow
flavor_text: TAILLOW courageously stands its ground against foes, however strong they may be. This gutsy POKÃ©MON will remain defiant even after a loss. On the other hand, it cries loudly if it becomes hungry.

name: swellow
flavor_text: SWELLOW flies high above our heads, making graceful arcs in the sky. This POKÃ©MON dives at a steep angle as soon as it spots its prey. The hapless prey is tightly grasped by SWELLOWâs clawed feet, preventing escape.

name: wingull
flavor_text: WINGULL has the habit of carrying prey and valuables in its beak and hiding them in all sorts of locations. This POKÃ©MON rides the winds and flies as if it were skating across the sky.

name: pelipper
flavor_text: It is a messenger of the skies, carrying small PokÃ©mon and eggs to safety in its bill.

name: ralts
flavor_text: RALTS senses the emotions of people using the horns on its head. This POKÃ©MON rarely appears before people. But when it does, it draws closer if it senses that the person has a positive disposition.

name: kirlia
flavor_text: It is said that a KIRLIA that is exposed to the positive emotions of its TRAINER grows beautiful. This POKÃ©MON controls psychokinetic powers with its highly developed brain.

name: gardevoir
flavor_text: GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the future. If it senses impending danger to its TRAINER, this POKÃ©MON is said to unleash its psychokinetic energy at full power.

name: surskit
flavor_text: From the tips of its feet, SURSKIT secretes an oil that enables it to walk on water as if it were skating. This POKÃ©MON feeds on microscopic organisms in ponds and lakes.

name: masquerain
flavor_text: MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This POKÃ©MON flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction - even sideways and backwards - as if it were a helicopter.

name: shroomish
flavor_text: SHROOMISH live in damp soil in the dark depths of forests. They are often found keeping still under fallen leaves. This POKÃ©MON feeds on compost that is made up of fallen, rotted leaves.

name: breloom
flavor_text: BRELOOM closes in on its foe with light and sprightly footwork, then throws punches with its stretchy arms. This POKÃ©MONâs fighting technique puts boxers to shame.

name: slakoth
flavor_text: SLAKOTH lolls around for over twenty hours every day. Because it moves so little, it does not need much food. This POKÃ©MONâs sole daily meal consists of just three leaves.

name: vigoroth
flavor_text: VIGOROTH is always itching and agitated to go on a wild rampage. It simply canât tolerate sitting still for even a minute. This POKÃ©MONâs stress level rises if it canât be moving constantly.

name: slaking
flavor_text: SLAKING spends all day lying down and lolling about. It eats grass growing within its reach. If it eats all the grass it can reach, this POKÃ©MON reluctantly moves to another spot.

name: nincada
flavor_text: NINCADA lives underground for many years in complete darkness. This POKÃ©MON absorbs nutrients from the roots of trees. It stays motionless as it waits for evolution.

name: ninjask
flavor_text: NINJASK moves around at such a high speed that it cannot be seen, even while its crying can be clearly heard. For that reason, this POKÃ©MON was long believed to be invisible.

name: shedinja
flavor_text: SHEDINJAâs hard body doesnât move - not even a twitch. In fact, its body appears to be merely a hollow shell. It is believed that this POKÃ©MON will steal the spirit of anyone peering into its hollow body from its back.

name: whismur
flavor_text: Normally, WHISMURâs voice is very quiet - it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention. However, if this POKÃ©MON senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume.

name: loudred
flavor_text: LOUDREDâs bellowing can completely decimate a wood-frame house. It uses its voice to punish its foes. This POKÃ©MONâs round ears serve as loudspeakers.

name: exploud
flavor_text: EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the tremors it creates by bellowing. If this POKÃ©MON violently inhales from the ports on its body, itâs a sign that it is preparing to let loose a huge bellow.

name: makuhita
flavor_text: MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will keep getting up and attacking its foe however many times it is knocked down. Every time it gets back up, this POKÃ©MON stores more energy in its body for evolving.

name: hariyama
flavor_text: It has the habit of challenging others without hesitation to tests of strength. Itâs been known to stand on train tracks and stop trains using forearm thrusts.

name: azurill
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon that lives by water. It moves quickly on land by bouncing on its big tail.

name: nosepass
flavor_text: NOSEPASSâs magnetic nose is always pointed to the north. If two of these POKÃ©MON meet, they cannot turn their faces to each other when they are close because their magnetic noses repel one another.

name: skitty
flavor_text: SKITTY has the habit of becoming fascinated by moving objects and chasing them around. This POKÃ©MON is known to chase after its own tail and become dizzy.

name: delcatty
flavor_text: DELCATTY prefers to live an unfettered existence in which it can do as it pleases at its own pace. Because this POKÃ©MON eats and sleeps whenever it decides, its daily routines are completely random.

name: sableye
flavor_text: SABLEYE lead quiet lives deep inside caverns. They are feared, however, because these POKÃ©MON are thought to steal the spirits of people when their eyes burn with a sinister glow in the darkness.

name: mawile
flavor_text: MAWHILEâs huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed. Its docile-looking face serves to lull its foe into letting down its guard. When the foe least expects it, MAWHILE chomps it with its gaping jaws.

name: aron
flavor_text: This POKÃ©MON has a body of steel. To make its body, ARON feeds on iron ore that it digs from mountains. Occasionally, it causes major trouble by eating bridges and rails.

name: lairon
flavor_text: LAIRON tempers its steel body by drinking highly nutritious mineral springwater until it is bloated. This POKÃ©MON makes its nest close to springs of delicious water.

name: aggron
flavor_text: AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment. This POKÃ©MON vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.

name: meditite
flavor_text: MEDITITE undertakes rigorous mental training deep in the mountains. However, whenever it meditates, this POKÃ©MON always loses its concentration and focus. As a result, its training never ends.

name: medicham
flavor_text: It is said that through meditation, MEDICHAM heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense. This POKÃ©MON hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.

name: electrike
flavor_text: ELECTRIKE stores electricity in its long body hair. This POKÃ©MON stimulates its leg muscles with electric charges. These jolts of power give its legs explosive acceleration performance.

name: manectric
flavor_text: MANECTRIC is constantly discharging electricity from its mane. The sparks sometimes ignite forest fires. When it enters a battle, this POKÃ©MON creates thunderclouds.

name: plusle
flavor_text: PLUSLE always acts as a cheerleader for its partners. Whenever a teammate puts out a good effort in battle, this POKÃ©MON shorts out its body to create the crackling noises of sparks to show its joy.

name: minun
flavor_text: MINUN is more concerned about cheering on its partners than its own safety. It shorts out the electricity in its body to create brilliant showers of sparks to cheer on its teammates.

name: volbeat
flavor_text: With the arrival of night, VOLBEAT emits light from its tail. It communicates with others by adjusting the intensity and flashing of its light. This POKÃ©MON is attracted by the sweet aroma of ILLUMISE.

name: illumise
flavor_text: With its sweet aroma, it guides Volbeat to draw signs with light in the night sky.

name: roselia
flavor_text: ROSELIA shoots sharp thorns as projectiles at any opponent that tries to steal the flowers on its arms. The aroma of this POKÃ©MON brings serenity to living things.

name: gulpin
flavor_text: Virtually all of GULPINâs body is its stomach. As a result, it can swallow something its own size. This POKÃ©MONâs stomach contains a special fluid that digests anything.

name: swalot
flavor_text: When SWALOT spots prey, it spurts out a hideously toxic fluid from its pores and sprays the target. Once the prey has weakened, this POKÃ©MON gulps it down whole with its cavernous mouth.

name: carvanha
flavor_text: CARVANHAâs strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POKÃ©MON.

name: sharpedo
flavor_text: Nicknamed âthe bully of the sea,â SHARPEDO is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediately if they snap off. Just one of these POKÃ©MON can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker.

name: wailmer
flavor_text: WAILMERâs nostrils are located above its eyes. This playful POKÃ©MON loves to startle people by forcefully snorting out seawater it stores inside its body out of its nostrils.

name: wailord
flavor_text: WAILORD is the largest of all identified POKÃ©MON up to now. This giant POKÃ©MON swims languorously in the vast open sea, eating massive amounts of food at once with its enormous mouth.

name: numel
flavor_text: NUMEL is extremely dull witted - it doesnât notice being hit. However, it canât stand hunger for even a second. This POKÃ©MONâs body is a seething cauldron of boiling magma.

name: camerupt
flavor_text: CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body. Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses through its body. Occasionally, the humps on this POKÃ©MONâs back erupt, spewing the superheated magma.

name: torkoal
flavor_text: You can tell how itâs feeling by the smoke spouting from its shell. Tremendous velocity is a sign of good health.

name: spoink
flavor_text: SPOINK bounces around on its tail. The shock of its bouncing makes its heart pump. As a result, this POKÃ©MON cannot afford to stop bouncing - if it stops, its heart will stop.

name: grumpig
flavor_text: GRUMPIG uses the black pearls on its body to amplify its psychic power waves for gaining total control over its foe. When this POKÃ©MON uses its special power, its snorting breath grows labored.

name: spinda
flavor_text: No two Spinda have the same pattern of spots. Its tottering step fouls the aim of foes.

name: trapinch
flavor_text: TRAPINCHâs nest is a sloped, bowl-like pit dug in sand. This POKÃ©MON patiently waits for prey to tumble down the pit. Its giant jaws have enough strength to crush even boulders.

name: vibrava
flavor_text: To make prey faint, VIBRAVA generates ultrasonic waves by vigorously making its two wings vibrate. This POKÃ©MONâs ultrasonic waves are so powerful, they can bring on headaches in people.

name: flygon
flavor_text: FLYGON is nicknamed âthe elemental spirit of the desert.â Because its flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand, this POKÃ©MON is always enveloped in a sandstorm while flying.

name: cacnea
flavor_text: CACNEA lives in arid locations such as deserts. It releases a strong aroma from its flower to attract prey. When prey comes near, this POKÃ©MON shoots sharp thorns from its body to bring the victim down.

name: cacturne
flavor_text: During the daytime, CACTURNE remains unmoving so that it does not lose any moisture to the harsh desert sun. This POKÃ©MON becomes active at night when the temperature drops.

name: swablu
flavor_text: SWABLU has light and fluffy wings that are like cottony clouds. This POKÃ©MON is not frightened of people. It lands on the heads of people and sits there like a cotton-fluff hat.

name: altaria
flavor_text: ALTARIA dances and wheels through the sky among billowing, cotton-like clouds. By singing melodies in its crystal-clear voice, this POKÃ©MON makes its listeners experience dreamy wonderment.

name: zangoose
flavor_text: Memories of battling its arch-rival SEVIPER are etched into every cell of ZANGOOSEâs body. This POKÃ©MON adroitly dodges attacks with incredible agility.

name: seviper
flavor_text: SEVIPER shares a generations-long feud with ZANGOOSE. The scars on its body are evidence of vicious battles. This POKÃ©MON attacks using its sword- edged tail.

name: lunatone
flavor_text: LUNATONE was discovered at a location where a meteorite fell. As a result, some people theorize that this POKÃ©MON came from space. However, no one has been able to prove this theory so far.

name: solrock
flavor_text: Solar energy is the source of its power, so it is strong during the daytime. When it spins, its body shines.

name: barboach
flavor_text: BARBOACHâs sensitive whiskers serve as a superb radar system. This POKÃ©MON hides in mud, leaving only its two whiskers exposed while it waits for prey to come along.

name: whiscash
flavor_text: WHISCASH is extremely territorial. Just one of these POKÃ©MON will claim a large pond as its exclusive territory. If a foe approaches it, it thrashes about and triggers a massive earthquake.

name: corphish
flavor_text: Its hardy vitality enables it to adapt to any environment. Its pincers will never release prey.

name: crawdaunt
flavor_text: CRAWDAUNT has an extremely violent nature that compels it to challenge other living things to battle. Other life-forms refuse to live in ponds inhabited by this POKÃ©MON, making them desolate places.

name: baltoy
flavor_text: BALTOY moves while spinning around on its one foot. Primitive wall paintings depicting this POKÃ©MON living among people were discovered in some ancient ruins.

name: claydol
flavor_text: CLAYDOL are said to be dolls of mud made by primitive humans and brought to life by exposure to a mysterious ray. This POKÃ©MON moves about while levitating.

name: lileep
flavor_text: LILEEP became extinct approximately a hundred million years ago. This ancient POKÃ©MON attaches itself to a rock on the seafloor and catches approaching prey using tentacles shaped like flower petals.

name: cradily
flavor_text: CRADILY roams around the ocean floor in search of food. This POKÃ©MON freely extends its tree trunk-like neck and captures unwary prey using its eight tentacles.

name: anorith
flavor_text: ANORITH was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive POKÃ©MON once lived in warm seas. It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws.

name: armaldo
flavor_text: ARMALDOâs tough armor makes all attacks bounce off. This POKÃ©MONâs two enormous claws can be freely extended or contracted. They have the power to punch right through a steel slab.

name: feebas
flavor_text: FEEBASâs fins are ragged and tattered from the start of its life. Because of its shoddy appearance, this POKÃ©MON is largely ignored. It is capable of living in both the sea and in rivers.

name: milotic
flavor_text: Its lovely scales are described as rainbow colored. They change color depending on the viewing angle.

name: castform
flavor_text: CASTFORMâs appearance changes with the weather. This POKÃ©MON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

name: kecleon
flavor_text: It changes body color to blend in with its surroundings. It also changes color if it is happy or sad.

name: shuppet
flavor_text: SHUPPET is attracted by feelings of jealousy and vindictiveness. If someone develops strong feelings of vengeance, this POKÃ©MON will appear in a swarm and line up beneath the eaves of that personâs home.

name: banette
flavor_text: BANETTE generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking pins into its own body. This POKÃ©MON was originally a pitiful plush doll that was thrown away.

name: duskull
flavor_text: DUSKULL can pass through any wall no matter how thick it may be. Once this POKÃ©MON chooses a target, it will doggedly pursue the intended victim until the break of dawn.

name: dusclops
flavor_text: DUSCLOPSâs body is completely hollow - there is nothing at all inside. It is said that its body is like a black hole. This POKÃ©MON will absorb anything into its body, but nothing will ever come back out.

name: tropius
flavor_text: The bunches of fruit around TROPIUSâs neck are very popular with children. This POKÃ©MON loves fruit, and eats it continuously. Apparently, its love for fruit resulted in its own outgrowth of fruit.

name: chimecho
flavor_text: CHIMECHO makes its cries echo inside its hollow body. When this POKÃ©MON becomes enraged, its cries result in ultrasonic waves that have the power to knock foes flying.

name: absol
flavor_text: Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POKÃ©MON.

name: wynaut
flavor_text: WYNAUT can always be seen with a big, happy smile on its face. Look at its tail to determine if it is angry. When angered, this POKÃ©MON will be slapping the ground with its tail.

name: snorunt
flavor_text: SNORUNT live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this POKÃ©MON steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns.

name: glalie
flavor_text: GLALIE has a body made of rock, which it hardens with an armor of ice. This POKÃ©MON has the ability to freeze moisture in the atmosphere into any shape it desires.

name: spheal
flavor_text: SPHEAL is much faster rolling than walking to get around. When groups of this POKÃ©MON eat, they all clap at once to show their pleasure. Because of this, their mealtimes are noisy.

name: sealeo
flavor_text: SEALEO has the habit of always juggling on the tip of its nose anything it sees for the first time. This POKÃ©MON occasionally entertains itself by balancing and rolling a SPHEAL on its nose.

name: walrein
flavor_text: It swims through icy seas while shattering ice floes with its large tusks. It is protected by its thick blubber.

name: clamperl
flavor_text: CLAMPERLâs sturdy shell is not only good for protection - it is also used for clamping and catching prey. A fully grown CLAMPERLâs shell will be scored with nicks and scratches all over.

name: huntail
flavor_text: HUNTAILâs presence went unnoticed by people for a long time because it lives at extreme depths in the sea. This POKÃ©MONâs eyes can see clearly even in the murky dark depths of the ocean.

name: gorebyss
flavor_text: GOREBYSS lives in the southern seas at extreme depths. Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure of water at incredible depths. Because of this, this POKÃ©MONâs body is unharmed by ordinary attacks.

name: relicanth
flavor_text: RELICANTH is a POKÃ©MON species that existed for a hundred million years without ever changing its form. This ancient POKÃ©MON feeds on microscopic organisms with its toothless mouth.

name: luvdisc
flavor_text: LUVDISC live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped POKÃ©MON earned its name by swimming after loving couples it spotted in the oceanâs waves.

name: bagon
flavor_text: Dreaming of one day flying, it practices by leaping off cliffs every day.

name: shelgon
flavor_text: Inside SHELGONâs armor-like shell, cells are in the midst of transformation to create an entirely new body. This POKÃ©MONâs shell is extremely heavy, making its movements sluggish.

name: salamence
flavor_text: SALAMENCE came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this POKÃ©MONâs cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

name: beldum
flavor_text: Instead of blood, a powerful magnetic force courses throughout BELDUMâs body. This POKÃ©MON communicates with others by sending controlled pulses of magnetism.

name: metang
flavor_text: When two BELDUM fuse together, METANG is formed. The brains of the BELDUM are joined by a magnetic nervous system. By linking its brains magnetically, this POKÃ©MON generates strong psychokinetic power.

name: metagross
flavor_text: METAGROSS has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer. This POKÃ©MON can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

name: regirock
flavor_text: Its entire body is made of rock. If any part chips off in battle, it attaches rocks to repair itself.

name: regice
flavor_text: REGICEâs body was made during an ice age. The deep-frozen body canât be melted, even by fire. This POKÃ©MON controls frigid air of minus 328 degrees F.

name: registeel
flavor_text: REGISTEEL has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this POKÃ©MON eats.

name: latias
flavor_text: LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKÃ©MON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

name: latios
flavor_text: LATIOS has the ability to make its foe see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head. This POKÃ©MON is intelligent and understands human speech.

name: kyogre
flavor_text: KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours. This POKÃ©MON saved people who were suffering from droughts.

name: groudon
flavor_text: GROUDON has long been described in mythology as the POKÃ©MON that raised lands and expanded continents. This POKÃ©MON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.

name: rayquaza
flavor_text: RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earthâs ozone layer, never descending to the ground. This POKÃ©MON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.

name: jirachi
flavor_text: A legend states that JIRACHI will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens. If this POKÃ©MON senses danger, it will fight without awakening.

name: deoxys
flavor_text: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKÃ©MONâs chest appears to be its brain.

name: turtwig
flavor_text: Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when it drinks water. It lives along lakes.

name: grotle
flavor_text: It knows where pure water wells up. It carries fellow PokÃ©mon there on its back.

name: torterra
flavor_text: Small PokÃ©mon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: chimchar
flavor_text: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.

name: monferno
flavor_text: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.

name: infernape
flavor_text: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.

name: piplup
flavor_text: Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: prinplup
flavor_text: It lives alone, away from others. Apparently, every one of them believes it is the most important.

name: empoleon
flavor_text: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: starly
flavor_text: They flock in great numbers. Though small, they flap their wings with great power.

name: staravia
flavor_text: It flies around forests and fields in search of bug PokÃ©mon. It stays within a huge flock.

name: staraptor
flavor_text: It has a savage nature. It will courageously challenge foes that are much larger.

name: bidoof
flavor_text: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.

name: bibarel
flavor_text: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: kricketot
flavor_text: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.

name: kricketune
flavor_text: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: shinx
flavor_text: All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: luxio
flavor_text: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.

name: luxray
flavor_text: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.

name: budew
flavor_text: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: roserade
flavor_text: It attracts prey with a sweet aroma, then downs it with thorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: cranidos
flavor_text: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.

name: rampardos
flavor_text: Its powerful head butt has enough power to shatter even the most durable things upon impact.

name: shieldon
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon that lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its facial hide is extremely hard.

name: bastiodon
flavor_text: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile PokÃ©mon that feeds on grass and berries.

name: burmy
flavor_text: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.

name: wormadam
flavor_text: When BURMY evolved, its cloak became a part of this PokÃ©monâs body. The cloak is never shed.

name: mothim
flavor_text: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by COMBEE.

name: combee
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to VESPIQUEN.

name: vespiquen
flavor_text: Its abdomen is a honeycomb for grubs. It raises its grubs on honey collected by COMBEE.

name: pachirisu
flavor_text: It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity. It stores them with berries in tree holes.

name: buizel
flavor_text: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.

name: floatzel
flavor_text: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.

name: cherubi
flavor_text: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.

name: cherrim
flavor_text: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.

name: shellos
flavor_text: Its colors and shapes differ from region to region. In the Sinnoh region, two types are confirmed.

name: gastrodon
flavor_text: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.

name: ambipom
flavor_text: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.

name: drifloon
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon formed by the spirits of people and PokÃ©mon. It loves damp, humid seasons.

name: drifblim
flavor_text: At dusk, swarms of them are carried aloft on winds. When noticed, they suddenly vanish.

name: buneary
flavor_text: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: lopunny
flavor_text: An extremely cautious PokÃ©mon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

name: mismagius
flavor_text: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.

name: honchkrow
flavor_text: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous MURKROW in tow.

name: glameow
flavor_text: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.

name: purugly
flavor_text: It is a brazen brute that barges its way into another PokÃ©monâs nest and claims it as its own.

name: chingling
flavor_text: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.

name: stunky
flavor_text: It protects itself by spraying a noxious fluid from its rear. The stench lingers for 24 hours.

name: skuntank
flavor_text: It sprays a vile-smelling fluid from the tip of its tail to attack. Its range is over 160 feet.

name: bronzor
flavor_text: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.

name: bronzong
flavor_text: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: bonsly
flavor_text: It looks as if it is always crying. It is actually adjusting its bodyâs fluid levels by eliminating excess.

name: mime jr.
flavor_text: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this PokÃ©mon.

name: happiny
flavor_text: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of CHANSEY.

name: chatot
flavor_text: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.

name: spiritomb
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

name: gible
flavor_text: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.

name: gabite
flavor_text: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.

name: garchomp
flavor_text: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

name: munchlax
flavor_text: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.

name: riolu
flavor_text: The aura that emanates from its body intensifies to alert others if it is afraid or sad.

name: lucario
flavor_text: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

name: hippopotas
flavor_text: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.

name: hippowdon
flavor_text: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.

name: skorupi
flavor_text: It grips prey with its tail claws and injects poison. It tenaciously hangs on until the poison takes.

name: drapion
flavor_text: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.

name: croagunk
flavor_text: Its cheeks hold poison sacs. It tries to catch foes off guard to jab them with toxic fingers.

name: toxicroak
flavor_text: Its knuckle claws secrete a toxin so vile that even a scratch could prove fatal.

name: carnivine
flavor_text: It attracts prey with its sweet- smelling saliva, then chomps down. It takes a whole day to eat prey.

name: finneon
flavor_text: After long exposure to sunlight, the patterns on its tail fins shine vividly when darkness arrives.

name: lumineon
flavor_text: It lives on the deep-sea floor. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its four tail fins.

name: mantyke
flavor_text: A friendly PokÃ©mon that captures the subtle flows of seawater using its two antennae.

name: snover
flavor_text: It lives on snowy mountains. Having had little contact with humans, it is boldly inquisitive.

name: abomasnow
flavor_text: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.

name: weavile
flavor_text: They live in cold regions, forming groups of four or five that hunt prey with impressive coordination.

name: magnezone
flavor_text: It evolved from exposure to a special magnetic field. Three units generate magnetism.

name: lickilicky
flavor_text: It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool.

name: rhyperior
flavor_text: It puts rocks in holes in its palms and uses its muscles to shoot them. GEODUDE are shot at rare times.

name: tangrowth
flavor_text: It ensnares prey by extending arms made of vines. Losing arms to predators does not trouble it.

name: electivire
flavor_text: As its electric charge amplifies, blue sparks begin to crackle between its horns.

name: magmortar
flavor_text: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600 degrees F from the ends of its arms. It lives in volcanic craters.

name: togekiss
flavor_text: It will never appear where there is strife. Its sightings have become rare recently.

name: yanmega
flavor_text: By churning its wings, it creates shock waves that inflict critical internal injuries to foes.

name: leafeon
flavor_text: Just like a plant, it uses photosynthesis. As a result, it is always enveloped in clear air.

name: glaceon
flavor_text: As a protective technique, it can completely freeze its fur to make its hairs stand like needles.

name: gliscor
flavor_text: It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!

name: mamoswine
flavor_text: Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.

name: porygon-z
flavor_text: Additional software was installed to make it a better PokÃ©mon. It began acting oddly, however.

name: gallade
flavor_text: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.

name: probopass
flavor_text: It freely controls three small units called Mini-Noses using magnetic force.

name: dusknoir
flavor_text: The antenna on its head captures radio waves from the world of spirits that command it to take people there.

name: froslass
flavor_text: It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.

name: rotom
flavor_text: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

name: uxie
flavor_text: Known as âThe Being of Knowledge.â It is said that it can wipe out the memory of those who see its eyes.

name: mesprit
flavor_text: Known as âThe Being of Emotion.â It taught humans the nobility of sorrow, pain, and joy.

name: azelf
flavor_text: Known as âThe Being of Willpower.â It sleeps at the bottom of a lake to keep the world in balance.

name: dialga
flavor_text: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.

name: palkia
flavor_text: It has the ability to distort space. It is described as a deity in Sinnoh-region mythology.

name: heatran
flavor_text: It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.

name: regigigas
flavor_text: There is an enduring legend that states this PokÃ©mon towed continents with ropes.

name: giratina
flavor_text: A PokÃ©mon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.

name: cresselia
flavor_text: Shiny particles are released from its wings like a veil. It is said to represent the crescent moon.

name: phione
flavor_text: It drifts in warm seas. It always returns to where it was born, no matter how far it may have drifted.

name: manaphy
flavor_text: Born on a cold seafloor, it will swim great distances to return to its birthplace.

name: darkrai
flavor_text: It can lull people to sleep and make them dream. It is active during nights of the new moon.

name: shaymin
flavor_text: It lives in flower patches and avoids detection by curling up to look like a flowering plant.

name: arceus
flavor_text: It is described in mythology as the PokÃ©mon that shaped the universe with its 1,000 arms.

name: victini
flavor_text: This PokÃ©mon brings victory. It is said that Trainers with Victini always win, regardless of the type of encounter.

name: snivy
flavor_text: It is very intelligent and calm. Being exposed to lots of sunlight makes its movements swifter.

name: servine
flavor_text: It moves along the ground as if sliding. Its swift movements befuddle its foes, and it then attacks with a vine whip.

name: serperior
flavor_text: It can stop its opponentsâ movements with just a glare. It takes in solar energy and boosts it internally.

name: tepig
flavor_text: It can deftly dodge its foeâs attacks while shooting fireballs from its nose. It roasts berries before it eats them.

name: pignite
flavor_text: When its internal fire flares up, its movements grow sharper and faster. When in trouble, it emits smoke.

name: emboar
flavor_text: It can throw a fire punch by setting its fists on fire with its fiery chin. It cares deeply about its friends.

name: oshawott
flavor_text: It fights using the scalchop on its stomach. In response to an attack, it retaliates immediately by slashing.

name: dewott
flavor_text: Strict training is how it learns its flowing double-scalchop technique.

name: samurott
flavor_text: One swing of the sword incorporated in its armor can fell an opponent. A simple glare from one of them quiets everybody.

name: patrat
flavor_text: Using food stored in cheek pouches, they can keep watch for days. They use their tails to communicate with others.

name: watchog
flavor_text: When they see an enemy, their tails stand high, and they spit the seeds of berries stored in their cheek pouches.

name: lillipup
flavor_text: It faces strong opponents with great courage. But, when at a disadvantage in a fight, this intelligent PokÃ©mon flees.

name: herdier
flavor_text: It has black, cape-like fur that is very hard and decreases the amount of damage it receives.

name: stoutland
flavor_text: It rescues people stranded by blizzards in the mountains. Its shaggy fur shields it from the cold.

name: purrloin
flavor_text: They steal from people for fun, but their victims canât help but forgive them. Their deceptively cute act is perfect.

name: liepard
flavor_text: These PokÃ©mon vanish and appear unexpectedly. Many Trainers are drawn to their beautiful form and fur.

name: pansage
flavor_text: This PokÃ©mon dwells deep in the forest. Eating a leaf from its head whisks weariness away as if by magic.

name: simisage
flavor_text: Ill tempered, it fights by swinging its barbed tail around wildly. The leaf growing on its head is very bitter.

name: pansear
flavor_text: When it is angered, the temperature of its head tuft reaches 600Â° F. It uses its tuft to roast berries.

name: simisear
flavor_text: It loves sweets because they become energy for the fire burning inside its body.

name: panpour
flavor_text: The water stored inside the tuft on its head is full of nutrients. Plants that receive its water grow large.

name: simipour
flavor_text: The tuft on its head holds water. When the level runs low, it replenishes the tuft by siphoning up water with its tail.

name: munna
flavor_text: Munna always float in the air. People whose dreams are eaten by them forget what the dreams had been about.

name: musharna
flavor_text: The mist emanating from their foreheads is packed with the dreams of people and PokÃ©mon.

name: pidove
flavor_text: Each follows its Trainerâs orders as best it can, but they sometimes fail to understand complicated commands.

name: tranquill
flavor_text: It can return to its Trainerâs location regardless of the distance separating them.

name: unfezant
flavor_text: Males swing their head plumage to threaten opponents. The femalesâ flying abilities surpass those of the males.

name: blitzle
flavor_text: When thunderclouds cover the sky, it will appear. It can catch lightning with its mane and store the electricity.

name: zebstrika
flavor_text: They have lightning-like movements. When Zebstrika run at full speed, the sound of thunder reverberates.

name: roggenrola
flavor_text: Its ear is hexagonal in shape. Compressed underground, its body is as hard as steel.

name: boldore
flavor_text: When it overflows with power, the orange crystal on its body glows. It looks for underground water in caves.

name: gigalith
flavor_text: Compressing the energy from its internal core lets it fire off an attack capable of blowing away a mountain.

name: woobat
flavor_text: Its habitat is dark forests and caves. It emits ultrasonic waves from its nose to learn about its surroundings.

name: swoobat
flavor_text: It emits sound waves of various frequencies from its nose, including some powerful enough to destroy rocks.

name: drilbur
flavor_text: It can dig through the ground at a speed of 30 mph. It could give a car running aboveground a good race.

name: excadrill
flavor_text: It can help in tunnel construction. Its drill has evolved into steel strong enough to bore through iron plates.

name: audino
flavor_text: It touches others with the feelers on its ears, using the sound of their heartbeats to tell how they are feeling.

name: timburr
flavor_text: It fights by swinging a piece of lumber around. It is close to evolving when it can handle the lumber without difficulty.

name: gurdurr
flavor_text: This PokÃ©mon is so muscular and strongly built that even a group of wrestlers could not make it budge an inch.

name: conkeldurr
flavor_text: It is thought that Conkeldurr taught humans how to make concrete more than 2,000 years ago.

name: tympole
flavor_text: They warn others of danger by vibrating their cheeks to create a high-pitched sound.

name: palpitoad
flavor_text: When they vibrate the bumps on their heads, they can make waves in water or earthquake-like vibrations on land.

name: seismitoad
flavor_text: They shoot paralyzing liquid from their head bumps. They use vibration to hurt their opponents.

name: throh
flavor_text: When it tightens its belt, it becomes stronger. Wild Throh use vines to weave their own belts.

name: sawk
flavor_text: The sound of Sawk punching boulders and trees can be heard all the way from the mountains where they train.

name: sewaddle
flavor_text: Leavanny dress it in clothes they made for it when it hatched. It hides its head in its hood while it is sleeping.

name: swadloon
flavor_text: Forests where Swadloon live have superb foliage because the nutrients they make from fallen leaves nourish the plant life.

name: leavanny
flavor_text: Upon finding a small PokÃ©mon, it weaves clothing for it from leaves, using the cutters on its arms and sticky silk.

name: venipede
flavor_text: Its bite injects a potent poison, enough to paralyze large bird PokÃ©mon that try to prey on it.

name: whirlipede
flavor_text: Protected by a hard shell, it spins its body like a wheel and crashes furiously into its enemies.

name: scolipede
flavor_text: With quick movements, it chases down its foes, attacking relentlessly with its horns until it prevails.

name: cottonee
flavor_text: When attacked, it escapes by shooting cotton from its body. The cotton serves as a decoy to distract the attacker.

name: whimsicott
flavor_text: Like the wind, it can slip through any gap, no matter how small. It leaves balls of white fluff behind.

name: petilil
flavor_text: The leaves on its head are very bitter. Eating one of these leaves is known to refresh a tired body.

name: lilligant
flavor_text: Even veteran Trainers face a challenge in getting its beautiful flower to bloom. This PokÃ©mon is popular with celebrities.

name: basculin
flavor_text: Red and blue Basculin get along so poorly, theyâll start fighting instantly. These PokÃ©mon are very hostile.

name: sandile
flavor_text: They live buried in the sands of the desert. The sun-warmed sands prevent their body temperature from dropping.

name: krokorok
flavor_text: They live in groups of a few individuals. Protective membranes shield their eyes from sandstorms.

name: krookodile
flavor_text: They never allow prey to escape. Their jaws are so powerful, they can crush the body of an automobile.

name: darumaka
flavor_text: When its internal fire is burning, it cannot calm down and it runs around. When the fire diminishes, it falls asleep.

name: darmanitan
flavor_text: Its internal fire burns at 2,500Â° F, making enough power that it can destroy a dump truck with one punch.

name: maractus
flavor_text: It uses an up-tempo song and dance to drive away the bird PokÃ©mon that prey on its flower seeds.

name: dwebble
